cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as pose estimation and object detection using Convolutional Neural Networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also deals with robotics applications, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.RO (Robotics). The use of neural networks and machine learning techniques also suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with analyzing error modes and object characteristics, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with multimedia applications such as object detection, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
